snippet.title: Dead Plate | RPG Maker Horror | No Commentary
snippet.description:
Game: Dead Plate
Find the game here: https://racheldrawsthis.itch.io/dead-plate
Original creator: STUDIO INVESTIGRAVE (racheldrawsthis)
Release Date: 2023
Engine: RPG Maker MV
I do NOT own anything on this video, all credit to their respective creators.

If the creator wants me to take this down, please tell me.

Endings Gotten: 4/4

A restaurant tycoon RPG maker horror game. Interesting but I'm not opposed to the idea. Cool game. Even if I kind of sucked at it. Art is good and story is interesting too. Good game. I just had to record this in 3 parts because my computer does not like recording MV Games for some reason.
